4 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
5 Sec. 1. INTENT
6 (a) It is the intent of the General Assembly that the Department of
7 Corrections ensures gender parity in the access to services and programs that
8 strengthen family connections.
9 (b) It is the further intent of the General Assembly that the Department of
10 Corrections develop a phased plan to expand the application of 28 V.S.A.
11 § 128 to all Vermont correctional facilities by 2028.
